en who, for a price, helped the Bolsheviks launder their loot, impoverish Russia, and impose their brutal will on millions.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aFinance, PublicxHistoryxSoviet Union. 0aFinance, PubliczSoviet UnionxHistory. 0aPillagexHistoryxSoviet Union. 0aPillagezSoviet UnionxHistory. 7aHISTORY / Russia & the Former Soviet Union.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311053799440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030015279140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300152791423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300152791/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles